snippet.title: World Series Baseball - Xbox 2002 (2002 AL East Rivals NYY vs BOS)
snippet.description:
This is a 2002 AL East Rivals between the New York Yankees and the Boston Red Sox on World Series Baseball for Xbox 2002.

World Series® Baseball takes the Xbox™ field with ultra-responsive controls and the deepest Franchise Mode in town. Throw in old school players and unis, advanced gameplay and more stats thank you know what to do with and you've got the ultimate hardball sim.
